author: Dalton Ross
title: Walking Dead clip: Rick encounters Saviors roadblock
text:
Email Gene Page/AMC 
All roads lead to the Saviors. Rick found that out the hard way in The Walking Dead ’s season 6 finale. And as this sneak peek of the Feb. 12 midseason premiere just released by AMC shows, any roads that don’t lead to the Saviors lead to Savior blockades and booby traps. 
Check out the video below as Rick and Co. find their path blocked. But then, as the group begins to move the cars out of the way, they discover something else entirely. Let’s just say this could prove to be an explosive situation. 
Andrew Lincoln tells EW that there will be bloodshed on the horizon. Will the first drops of blood be spilled here? We’ll have to wait to see the full scene on Sunday night to find out. 
The Walking Dead returns Sunday, Feb. 12 at 9 p.m. ET on AMC. Show Full Article
